io.spine.server.event

Class EventDispatch<I,E extends TransactionalEntity<I,?,?>,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.event.EventDispatch<I,E,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of entity ID
    E - the type of entity
    R - the type of the dispatch result

    @Internal
public final class EventDispatch<I,E extends TransactionalEntity<I,?,?>,R>
extends java.lang.Object
    A dispatch of the event to the appropriate handler of an entity.

    Unlike the DispatchCommand, this class is a simple wrapper around the BiFunction which performs an actual event dispatch.
